Title: Analysis of startup_stm32.s & Reset_Handler
Description: Understand what happens BEFORE main(): Stack Pointer init, .data/.bss initialization, clock setup. When RTOS crashes before main(), you need this knowledge.

Title: Experiment: volatile keyword & Compiler Optimization Effects
Description: Write a polling loop without volatile, compile with -O3, watch it hang. Understand why compiler optimizes away your busy-wait. CRITICAL embedded trap.

Title: Flash Wear Leveling & LittleFS Implementation
Description: Internal flash has ~10K write cycles. Logging every second = dead board in 3 hours! Implement LittleFS for safe data logging. Use SD cards for high-frequency writes.
AI Prompt: Help me implement LittleFS on STM32 internal flash with wear leveling.

Title: Compiler Flags Audit: FPU & Optimization
Description: Verify -mfloat-abi=hard is enabled. Without FPU, your DSP filter runs 50x slower in software emulation. Check -mcpu, -mfpu flags.
AI Prompt: Audit my compiler flags for DSP performance - am I using hardware FPU correctly?

Title: Clock Tree Configuration (RCC) - HSI to HSE Switch
Description: Internal oscillator has 1% drift causing UART garbage at high baud rates. Configure external crystal (HSE) and PLL for stable 168MHz operation.
AI Prompt: Guide me through STM32 clock tree: HSE -> PLL -> SYSCLK configuration.

Title: Power Rail Isolation for Motors/Actuators
Description: Motor current spikes drop USB voltage -> Brown-out Reset -> CPU reboots -> you think it's software bug. Learn power isolation and decoupling.

Title: Static Analysis with Cppcheck & Clang-Tidy
